### Tooling

- Use `pnpm` at repo root; run tasks with `turbo run <task>` (not npm/yarn).
- Workspace layout: [pnpm-workspace.yaml](pnpm-workspace.yaml) — `apps/*`, `packages/*`, `packages/helpers/*`.
- Package scope: `@companies/*` imports over deep relative paths when a package exists.
- Target one package: `pnpm --filter @companies/<name> <script>`.

### Commits

- Allowed scopes: `commitlint.scope-enum` in [package.json](package.json) (root).
